      "id": "heading1",
      "label": "Heading 2",
      "default": "Trufairs Verified – Trusted Quality You Can See"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "content",
      "label": "Content",
      "default": "<p>At Trufairs, we believe you deserve full confidence in the products you bring into your home. That's why we created Trufairs Verified. Each item featured in this section has been personally handled, tested, and inspected by our team to ensure it meets our quality standards.</p><p>Our products come directly from reliable manufacturers. Our product descriptions accurately reflect the item, ensuring our customers receive exactly what they expect. We strive to provide descriptions that are completely aligned with the product, guaranteeing customer satisfaction with every purchase on Trufairs.</p><p>We believe in transparency.That's why we test every product in a real life setting to capture authentic unedited images. No studio or fake tricks, just raw, real-life photos and videos from our product evaluations. Our commitment to authenticity is that each product is used and photographed in actual homes to provide you with a true-to-life preview.</p><p>We also provide clear installation guidance through step-by-step visuals to make setup simple and worry-free.</p><p>At Trufairs, our mission is to bring you high-quality products at honest, affordable prices, backed by real transparency and real proof.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "content1",
      "label": "Content 2",
      "default": "<p>At Trufairs, we believe you deserve full confidence in the products you bring into your home. That's why we created Trufairs Verified. Each item featured in this section has been personally handled, tested, and inspected by our team to ensure it meets our quality standards.</p><p>Our products come directly from reliable manufacturers. Our product descriptions accurately reflect the item, ensuring our customers receive exactly what they expect. We strive to provide descriptions that are completely aligned with the product, guaranteeing customer satisfaction with every purchase on Trufairs.</p><p>We believe in transparency.That's why we test every product in a real life setting to capture authentic unedited images. No studio or fake tricks, just raw, real-life photos and videos from our product evaluations. Our commitment to authenticity is that each product is used and photographed in actual homes to provide you with a true-to-life preview.</p><p>We also provide clear installation guidance through step-by-step visuals to make setup simple and worry-free.</p><p>At Trufairs, our mission is to bring you high-quality products at honest, affordable prices, backed by real transparency and real proof.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "tagline",
      "label": "Tagline",
      "default": "See it. Trust it. Love it.\nThat's Trufairs Verified."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "tagline1",
      "label": "Tagline 2",
      "default": "See it. Trust it. Love it.\nThat's Trufairs Verified."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Style Settings"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "background_color",
      "label": "Background Color",
      "default": "#ffffff"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "heading_color",
      "label": "Heading Color",
      "default": "#000000"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "heading_size",
      "label": "Heading Font Size",
      "min": 16,
